{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "第十四回\"雷电双神\"：沈璧君回到大明湖畔的沈家庄，发现庄院已化为瓦砾，悲痛欲绝。客栈伙计安慰她，提及萧十一郎并非坏人。黑暗中出现两个自称\"雷电双神\"的太湖高手——雷满堂与龙一闪，声称专程来为沈太君拜寿却来迟一步。他们告诉沈璧君，\"鲁东四义\"中的大侠和三侠已遇难，二侠沈天竹和四侠沈天菊身负重伤。沈璧君被带到船上探望伤者，沈天菊反复念叨\"萧十一郎，你好狠\"。此时萧十一郎出现，沈天菊指认他为凶手。沈璧君怒刺萧十一郎一刀，但他毫不闪避。雷满堂与龙一闪联手攻击萧十一郎，却被他轻松击败——龙一闪被沈天竹的暗器所杀，沈天竹也被长枪刺死。原来雷满堂早已奄奄一息，被小公子操控着冲入船舱。小公子现身，揭露真相：放火烧庄、杀害沈太夫人的正是她自己，雷电双神和鲁东四义都是被她收买来骗沈璧君的。沈璧君再次冤枉了萧十一郎，心如刀割。小公子透露她有一个极其厉害的师父，无人能挡其二十招，但她拒绝透露师父名字，以此缠住萧十一郎。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "事已如此，我看姑娘不如还是先回到小店去吧，无论怎么样，先和那位相公商量商量也好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "其实，那位相公并不是个坏人，他不肯送姑娘回来，也许就是怕姑娘见到这情况伤心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "瞧姑娘在此，莫是和金针沈家有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我姓沈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "姑娘和沈太君是怎么样个称呼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她老人家是我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "姑娘莫非就是连夫人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我方才已请教过两位的名姓，两位为何不肯说呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "果然是连夫人，请恕在下等失礼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "在下雷满堂，是太湖来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "在下姓龙名光，草字一闪，夫人多指教。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是雷大侠和龙二侠……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "在下等贱名何足挂齿，'侠'之一字，更是万万担当不起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位远从太湖而来，却不知有何要务？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "在下等本是专程赶来给太夫人拜寿的，却不料……竟来迟了一步。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我俩是两天前来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两天前……那时这里莫非已……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我兄弟来的时候，此间已起火，而且死伤满地，只恨我兄弟来迟一步，纵然用尽全力，也未能将这场火扑灭。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却不知受伤的是哪些人？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "当时'鲁东四义'恰巧都在府上作客，大侠、三侠已不幸遇难，二侠和四侠也已身负重伤。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了沈二侠和沈四侠外，还有谁负了伤？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "除了他两位外，就再也没有别人了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我那祖……祖……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "沈天柏与沈天竹就在那边船上，夫人何妨也到那边去歇着，再从长计议。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "夫人自己是否还能行走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "在下今年已近六十，夫人若不嫌冒昧，就由在下携扶夫人前去如何？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈二侠和沈四侠真的在那船上？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "夫人莫非信不过我兄弟？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我只是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "夫人身遭惨变，小心谨慎些，也本是应该的，何况，夫人从来就不认得我兄弟。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我绝不是这意思，只是……不知道沈二侠和沈四侠的伤重不重？是否可以说话？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "既然还未死，怎会不能开口说话？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "沈四侠两天来一直未曾合过眼，也一直未曾闭过嘴，他嘴里一直翻来覆去的念着一个人的名字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁的名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "自然是那凶手的名字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凶……手……是……谁？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "夫人既不信任我兄弟，在下纵然说出那凶手是谁，夫人也未必相信，不如还是自己去看看的好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "此间四下无人，夫人到了船上，也许还可放心些。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是……可是我又怎敢劳动两位呢？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "夫人就以这木板为轿，让我兄弟抬去如何？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "text": "跟着你来的是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "text": "哪有什么人？你莫非眼花了吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你是谁？干什么来的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "text": "老二，你还不出手？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢，这人是我的朋友……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……你怎会来的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我也不知道我怎会来的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是他！……是谁杀了他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "text": "你杀了他？为什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这位兄台既是夫人的朋友，在下也不便说什么了。只不过，杀他的人，绝不是我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "究竟是谁杀了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我二弟既然说没有杀他，就是没有杀他，'雷电双神'虽不是什么了不得的人物，却从来不说假话。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "龙一闪",
      "listener": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "text": "我兄弟是不是说谎的人，江湖中人人都知道，大哥又何必再说！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我二弟既未杀他，杀他的人是谁，夫人还不明白么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "难道是你杀了他？为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你认为我会杀他？你认为我会说谎？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……我……我不知道。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你当然不知道，你根本不认得我，为何要信任我？我只不过是个……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tian_ju",
      "speaker_name": "沈天菊",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我认得你……我认得你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_shen_tian_ju",
      "text": "你认得他？他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tian_ju",
      "speaker_name": "沈天菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他就是凶手！他就是萧十一郎！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……你真的是萧十一郎？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不错，我就是萧十一郎！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……你……你就是杀人的凶手？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我当然也杀过人，可是我并没有……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tian_ju",
      "speaker_name": "沈天菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我身上这一刀就是被他砍的，沈太夫人也死在他手上，他身上这把刀，就是杀人的凶器！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tian_ju",
      "speaker_name": "沈天菊",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "好，萧十一郎，想不到你也有今天……快，快，再给他一刀，我要看着他死在你手上。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tian_ju",
      "speaker_name": "沈天菊",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他就是杀死太夫人的凶手，你还等什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "夫人不愿出手，我来杀他也是一样！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "小心……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "好功夫，果然好功夫，若能再接我一凿，我也服了你！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你要我的命，我也要你的命，我去见阎王，好歹也得要你陪着。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "speaker_name": "雷满堂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "萧十一郎，你为何还不死，我正在等着你……你快死呀！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lei_man_tang",
      "text": "你用不着等我，我死不了的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "又是你，果然又是你！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错，又是我，我阴魂不散，缠定你了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我一天不见你，就想得要命，叫我不见你，那怎么行？叫我躲开你，除非杀了我……唉，杀了我也不行，我死也缠定了你这个人。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你……难道你也是个女人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你现在才知道么？我若是男人，又怎舍得对你那么狠心？只有女人才会对女人狠得下心来，这道理你都不明白？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这沈姑娘虽长得不错，其实却半点也不解风情，有哪点能比得上我，萧郎呀萧郎，你为什么偏偏要喜欢她，不喜欢我呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "哎呀，原来你受了伤，是谁刺伤了你，是谁这么狠心？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "是我刺伤了他，你杀了我吧。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "是你，不会吧？他对你这么好，你却要杀他？……我看你并不像这么没良心的女人呀。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "若是再有机会，我还是要杀他的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我和他仇深似海，我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他和你有仇？谁说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "鲁东四义、雷电双神，他们都是人证。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 754,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他救了你好几次命，你却不信任他，反而要去相信那些人的话。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 758
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "可是……可是他自己也亲口告诉过我，他就是萧十一郎。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不错，他的确是萧十一郎，但放火烧了你家屋子，杀了你祖母的人，却不是萧十一郎呀。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "不是他是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "当然是我，除了我还有谁做得出那些事？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "鲁东四义、雷电双神，都是被我收买了，故意来骗你的。我以为他们一定骗不过你，因为萧十一郎对你那么好，你怎会相信他们这些混账王八蛋的话？谁知你看来虽还不太笨，其实却偏偏是个不知好歹的呆子！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你现在又想死了，是不是？但你就算死了，又怎能补偿他对你的好处？若不是他，你早已不知死过多少次了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 798
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你既然要杀我，现在为什么不动手？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 802
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我本来的确是想杀你的，现在却改变了主意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 804
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "为……为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "因为我还要你多看看他，多想想你自己做的事……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "但我却不想再看她了，这种不知好歹的人，我看着就生气，你若真的喜欢我，就赶快将她赶走，赶得越远越好。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "为了你，我本来也想放她走的，只可惜我没这么大的胆子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 824
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 826,
      "line_end": 826
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你知道，她是我师父想要的人，我就算不能将她活生生的带回去，至少也得将她的尸体带回去才能交差。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 828,
      "line_end": 830
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你难道还想回去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 832,
      "line_end": 832
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我本来也想跟你一齐逃走的，逃得远远的，找个地方躲起来，恩恩爱爱的过一辈子，可是……我实在不敢不回去，你也不知道我那师父有多厉害，我就算躲到天涯海角，他也一定会找着我的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 834,
      "line_end": 838
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你师父是谁？他真有这么大的本事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 842
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他本事之大，说出来你也不会相信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 844,
      "line_end": 844
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我本事也不小呀。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "以你的武功，也许能挡得住他二三十招，但他在四十招之内，一定可以要你的命！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 848,
      "line_end": 850
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你未免也将我看得太不中用了吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 852,
      "line_end": 852
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "普天之下，没有哪一个人能挡得住他二十招的，你若真能在二十招内不落败，已经算很不错的了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 856
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我不信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 858,
      "line_end": 858
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不管你信不信，我也不会告诉你他的名字，你越想知道，我越不告诉你……我越不告诉你，你就越想知道，就只好每天缠着我打听，你越缠得我紧，我越高兴。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 860,
      "line_end": 862
    }
  ],
